{
  "text": "At the business level, enterprises focus on the design of collaborative processes to define and agree on the behavior of the inter-enterprise collaboration. A collaborative business process defines the global view of the interactions among enterprises to achieve common business goals [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
